## 1. Purpose of This Document
This transparency statement explains the conditions under which this project was developed, the constraints that shaped the final submission, and the rationale for providing the **Lite** version of Golden Governor v1.2.5 for evaluation.  
The goal is clarity — not excuses. The system presented here is complete, functional, and representative of the intended architecture.

